<figureCitation box="[271,343,1167,1191]" captionStart="FIGURES 30 – 37" captionStartId="6.[151,264,1432,1455]" captionTargetBox="[267,1301,215,1409]" captionTargetId="figure@6.[267,1319,193,1411]" captionTargetPageId="6" captionText="FIGURES 30 – 37. Habralebra gillettei Young: (30) forewing; (31) hind wing; (32) pygofer (lateral); (33) subgenital plate (lateroventral); (34) style (ventral); (35) style (lateral); (36) aedeagus and connective (ventral); (37) aedeagus (lateral)." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/283593/files/figure.png" pageId="5" pageNumber="44">
